phorward
------------------------------------------
phorward is a versatile C-library. It is split into several modules, and mostly
focuses on the definition and implementation of parsers, recognizers, virtual
machines and regular expressions.

Runtime requirements:
  bash-4.4.12-3
  cygwin-3.0.7-1
  libphorward-devel-1.0.0-1bl1
  libphorward0-1.0.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.6.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-7
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/phorward/phorward

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/phorward/phorward/archive/v1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack phorward-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./phorward-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/phorward-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/phorward-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libphorward0-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libphorward-devel-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(phorward)
  /usr/bin/pdoc
  /usr/bin/pinclude
  /usr/bin/plex.exe
  /usr/bin/pproto
  /usr/bin/pregex.exe
  /usr/bin/ptest
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/phorward.README
  /usr/share/doc/phorward/ChangeLog.md
  /usr/share/doc/phorward/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/phorward/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/phorward/TODO.md
  /usr/share/phorward/phorward.html

(libphorward0)
  /usr/bin/cygphorward-0.dll

(libphorward-devel)
  /usr/include/phorward.h
  /usr/lib/libphorward.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/phorward.pc

